{"id": 231972822, "title": "MPOLONJENI ROYAL KRAAL BURNT DOWN", "text": "The motive behind the arson attack is still unknown, but many suspect that it may be linked to the recent killing of Indvuna yemcuba Gamedze. \u2018Adding, the source said the community was devastated by the loss of their leader and the destruction of their sacred site, and they were calling for justice to be served. Further, the source mentioned that the burning of the Mpolonjeni Royal Kraal was a tragic event that had deeply affected the people of the area and Eswatini in general. \u201cIt serves as a reminder of the importance of preserving and protecting our cultural heritage, and the need to come together in times of crisis,\u201d said the source. Adding, the source said the community will continue to mourn the loss of their leader and their sacred site, but they will also remain resilient and united in the face of adversity.", "summary": "MANZINI - The Mpolonjeni Chiefdom Royal Kraal, was allegedly burnt down by unknown people.\nThe incident happened&nbsp; at Mpolonjeni Chiefdom in Siteki, in the early hours", "url": "http://www.times.co.sz/news/145527-mpolonjeni-royal-kraal-burnt-down.html", "image": null, "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 13:22:00", "author": null, "language": "en", "catgory": "entertainment", "source_country": "sz", "sentiment": -0.177}